1. *Umuknula* je u sebi pa se nije oglasila. (She hushed herself up and did not speak up.) 
2. Čuo sam *umukan* glas sa strane. (I heard a muffled voice from the side.)
3. On se *umuknuo* kada joj je rekao da će je ostaviti. (He became quiet when he told her he was going to leave her.)
4. Glasovi su se *umuknuli* kada su videli njenu tugu. (The voices became quiet when they saw her sorrow.)
5. Ona je *umuknula* kada je čula gorku istinu. (She quietened down when she heard the bitter truth.)